::FZ/Prowl/Perndabot/Repressor/Grimmler::

Since FZ was almost identical to Zardus, he recieves Angel Prime's 
transmission.

"I do fight my battles," FZ replies as Prowl barely flinches at FZ's 
punch, "Much better than you Maximals are doing."

FZ ducks under a swing from Prowl, coming back up with a strong 
uppercut and hitting Prowl. This time Prowl stumbles back. Prowl 
could sense Manterror flying toward him, and he could also feel 
several bots ganging up on Iron Raptor.

Prowl flipps backwards, powering his boosters. Flying upside down 
(back to the ground), Prowl heads for Iron Raptor's position, leaving 
FZ in a clowd of exaust.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prendabot jumps back as dirt covers his optics, whiping them off. He 
sees Nemesis Enforcer open fire on Iron Raptor.

Perndabot jumps toward Iron Raptor, slashing down his sword. Before 
his sword comes close to hitting the Maximal commander, something 
explodes against Perndabot's side, sending the Alliance bot flying 
sideways before crashing to the ground.

Prowl zooms by, heading for Perndabot, who was furioustly getting to 
his feet. FZ zooms by seconds later, following after Prowl.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Repressor touches down and transforms, his hand cluching a leaking 
side. He looks up to see Grimmler aiming at him.

Repressor drops to the ground, barely avoiding Grimmler's shot.
